Title: WANTED: Lieutenant Ethan Jacobson
Description:
Wanted for crimes against the Domination Point forces!

Lieutenant Ethan Jacobson is responsible for leading several ground assaults against the Bilgewater lumber operation.

Last spotted occupying an island south of Quickchop's Lumber Farm.
ObjectivesText: Destroy Lieutenant Ethan Jacobson in the Southern Isles south of Quickchop's Lumber Farm.
